description:
Opie & Jim Norton SEP 15 2015 Tue (03:09:38) 


On today's show: Jim Florentine & Sammy Hagar. 

Today on Opie and Jimmy, we start the show with Jim Florentine in studio. We discuss Donald Trump, we listen to some clips of Hillary Clinton, we listen to some clips of Donald Trump, we talk about Eli Manning, and we read about old torture devices. 

We discuss Ron White, we listen to Sarah Silverman discuss comedians changing, we talk about PC culture, and we talk more about torture devices. 

Jim Florentine talks about meeting football players, the singer of Devo has a 9/11 cake at his wedding, a topless toddler is in Times Square, we discuss sugar, and Jim's kid wants to be in a band. 

Sandy Kane calls in, and Sammy Hagar stops by
